name: A Crystalline Moment
description: A field of shimmering Amethyst crystal captured with glorious stereoscopic 3D photography. Single Edition Hi-Res GIF by Sarah Zucker.
collection_description: SuperRare makes it easy to create, sell, and collect rare digital art.
